Loading the Income per person (GDP/capita, PPP$ inflation-adjusted) data and merging it with the gapminder data

gdp=read.csv('income_per_person_gdppercapita_ppp_inflation_adjusted.csv')
gdp=merge(x=continent_df, y=gdp)
gdp=na.omit(gdp)
pop_df = read.csv('population_total.csv')
pop_df=merge(x=continent_df, y=pop_df)
pop_df=na.omit(pop_df)
pop = select(pop_df, 'country', 'continent')
pop$pop_X1960 = pop_df$X1960
pop$pop_X1980 = pop_df$X1980
pop$pop_X2000 = pop_df$X2000
pop$pop_X2020 = pop_df$X2020

gdp_df = merge(x=select(gdp,'country',"continent", "X1960", "X1980", "X2000", "X2020" ), y=select(pop,'country',"continent", "pop_X1960", "pop_X1980", "pop_X2000", "pop_X2020" ))

gdp_temp = gdp_df
gdp_temp$growth_percent = ((gdp_temp$X2020 / gdp_temp$X1960) ^ (1/(2020-1960))-1) * 100
gdp_temp$growth_1960_1980 = ((gdp_temp$X1980 / gdp_temp$X1960) ^ (1/(20))-1) * 100
gdp_temp$growth_1980_2000 = ((gdp_temp$X2000 / gdp_temp$X1980) ^ (1/(20))-1) * 100
gdp_temp$growth_2000_2020 = ((gdp_temp$X2020 / gdp_temp$X2000) ^ (1/(20))-1) * 100

gdp_df$X1960 = as.numeric(gdp_df$X1960) * as.numeric(gdp_df$pop_X1960)
gdp_df$X1980 = as.numeric(gdp_df$X1980) * as.numeric(gdp_df$pop_X1980)
gdp_df$X2000 = as.numeric(gdp_df$X2000) * as.numeric(gdp_df$pop_X2000)
gdp_df$X2020 = as.numeric(gdp_df$X2020) * as.numeric(gdp_df$pop_X2020)

gdp_df = setNames(aggregate(list( gdp_df$X1960, gdp_df$X1980, gdp_df$X2000, gdp_df$X2020, gdp_df$pop_X1960, gdp_df$pop_X1980, gdp_df$pop_X2000, gdp_df$pop_X2020), by = list(gdp_df$continent),sum ), c("continent", "X1960", "X1980", "X2000", "X2020","pop_X1960", "pop_X1980", "pop_X2000", "pop_X2020"))

gdp_df$X1960 = as.numeric(gdp_df$X1960) / as.numeric(gdp_df$pop_X1960)
gdp_df$X1980 = as.numeric(gdp_df$X1980)/ as.numeric(gdp_df$pop_X1980)
gdp_df$X2000 = as.numeric(gdp_df$X2000) / as.numeric(gdp_df$pop_X2000)
gdp_df$X2020 = as.numeric(gdp_df$X2020) / as.numeric(gdp_df$pop_X2020)

gdp_df = select(gdp_df, 'continent', 'X1960',"X1980", "X2000", "X2020")

gdp_df$growth_percent = ((gdp_df$X2020 / gdp_df$X1960) ^ (1/(2020-1960))-1) * 100
gdp_df$growth_1960_1980 = ((gdp_df$X1980 / gdp_df$X1960) ^ (1/(20))-1) * 100
gdp_df$growth_1980_2000 = ((gdp_df$X2000 / gdp_df$X1980) ^ (1/(20))-1) * 100

Comparing the growth rates from a common initial point

temp=desc_gdp_growth
years=c(1960:2020)

desc_gdp_growth1=desc_gdp_growth
desc_gdp_growth1=desc_gdp_growth1[rep(seq_len(nrow(desc_gdp_growth)), length(years)), ]

sort_key=factor(desc_gdp_growth1$country, levels = temp$country)
desc_gdp_growth1=desc_gdp_growth1[order(sort_key),]
years=rep(c(1960:2020),10)
years=sort(years)

desc_gdp_growth1$X1960 = desc_gdp_growth1$X1960*0+1

desc_gdp_growth1$gdp_calc= desc_gdp_growth1$X1960 * (1 + (desc_gdp_growth1$growth_percent/100)) ^ (unique(years)-1960) 

desc_gdp_growth1$year=rep(c(1960:2020),10)

ggplot(desc_gdp_growth1,aes(x=year, y=gdp_calc, color=country, group=country)) + geom_point() + geom_line() + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1, size=16), axis.text.y = element_text(size=16), axis.title.x = element_text(size=16), axis.title.y = element_text(size=16), plot.title = element_text(size=20)) + xlab('Year') + ylab('Estimated GDP per capita (USD)') + ggtitle('GDP growth in 10 fastest growing countries measured at common origin') + scale_color_manual(values = cb_palette)
